    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>pepper pieces</strong> and <strong>Cumberland</strong> <strong>sausages</strong> to a baking tray</p><p>Put the tray in the oven for an initial 20 min or until the sausages are starting to brown</p>",
      "order": 3,
