      "instruction": "<p>Drain and pat the <strong>mozzarella </strong>dry with kitchen paper (squeeze as much liquid out as you can)</p><p>Tear the <strong>drained mozzarella</strong> into rough, bite-sized pieces</p><p>Wash the <strong>baby leaf salad</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p>",
